1:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fa288d208850c404abeabfdd584baba05e74fc","tid":1196513,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d4c5297895d86c9ef38c1a5588767a3582528f","tid":1196513,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:23:32.000Z","msg":"連登好多人都知和理非冇用，但冇經驗而且唔夠決心，需要有人帶領"},{"pid":"5948050196fab97695ab434590fc95f954ac2d2a","tid":1196513,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc480b31b5638b0e15ffed5e1cbbe01b83e95ef","tid":1196513,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:34:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼得2種<br />\n黑社會同狗<br />\n我地用左5年時間黎學識分辨人定鬼<br />\n望下你周圍其實係冇鬼<br />\n有都唔會係廿歲 大學生<br />\n唔好亂標籤其他人係鬼,或者影相捉鬼<br />\n分化技倆大家見唔少,都開始免疫<br />\n<br />\n係唔係開始要開返tg group呢?<br />\n通訊同時保護好自己<br />\n<br />\n大家都開始發現,所有狗唔係無辜<br />\n對方冇留過情,我地手下亦唔需要留情<br />\n唔好再妄想和理非可以解決問題<br />\n已經用左兩次既機會黎感化各界<br />\n而結果係大家都討論過,咁點?<br />\n<br />\n就係柒婆屌你屎忽屌到啪啪聲<br />\n仲要話你蘿柚唔夠趷<br />\n<br />\n咁黎緊方向決定到,係時候籌備<br />\n同諗下用咩方法<br />\n<blockquote>大家可以加志同道合既tg group<br />\n到時想打遊擊定衝擊佔領 任君選擇</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7bc9e24aeccc775771c48cb50028a91dc8fb8d6a","tid":1196513,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}